### 결제 요청
POST {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/payments
X-Loopers-LoginId: user@loopers.com
X-Loopers-LoginPw: password123!
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "{{orderId}}",
  "cardType": "SAMSUNG",
  "cardNo": "1234-5678-9814-1451"
}

### 결제 결과 콜백 (PG → commerce-api, 테스트용 직접 호출)
POST {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/payments/callback
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionKey": "20260624:TR:abc123",
  "orderId": "{{orderId}}",
  "cardType": "SAMSUNG",
  "cardNo": "1234-5678-9814-1451",
  "amount": 10000,
  "status": "SUCCESS",
  "reason": "정상 승인되었습니다."
}
